FirstRand Says Momentum Group's Unbundling Likely to Increase Its Earnings

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-03-02T06:04:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-02/firstrand-says-momentum-group-s-unbundling-likely-to-increase-its-earnings.html
  FirstRand Ltd . said the unbundling
of Momentum Group Ltd. resulted in a “significant non-recurring
gain” because of a dividend in specie and that earnings per
share for the six months through December will increase by 260
percent to 270 percent because of this.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
